History</st>

<p>

<list>
<entry level="1" type="bullet">

<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../553/34553.xml">
1999</link>: The visions and concepts, which eventually became Colayer, were worked out by founder, Markus Hegi, and a small working prototype was developed on his laptop.</entry>
<entry level="1" type="bullet">

<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../548/34548.xml">
2000</link>-<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../163/36163.xml">
2003</link>: Markus Hegi founded Metalayer AG, to work further on his ideas &amp; concepts. The development of these concepts started as a collaboration tool prototype, referred to as "The metalayer Comty Hub". Additionally, the exploration of suitable technologies were taken out for further scalability of the platform.</entry>
<entry level="1" type="bullet">

<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../524/35524.xml">
2004</link>-<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../164/36164.xml">
