<sec>
<st>
Colayer platform</st>
<p>

Colayer (or <b>Co</b>llaboration <b>layer</b>) is also the name of the product, it's a <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../191/1134191.xml">
social web software</link> that can be used to create a <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../597/627597.xml">
virtual organisation</link>.<ref xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#xpointer(//reflist/entry[@id=%222%22])">2</ref><ref xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#xpointer(//reflist/entry[@id=%223%22])">3</ref> The software integrates many communication needs of an organization. It offers <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../885/75885.xml">
content management system</link><ref xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#xpointer(//reflist/entry[@id=%224%22])">4</ref>, <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../384/1558384.xml">
virtual conferencing</link> (online meetings, email and SMS notification)<ref xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#xpointer(//reflist/entry[@id=%225%22])">5</ref>, reporting and statistical analysis.</p>

